improved_metadata.title: Avenue Dreams
improved_metadata.description: A raw portrayal of life in a struggling urban environment, where dreams clash with the harsh realities of poverty and survival. The lyrics depict a cycle of hardship, resilience, and the pursuit of freedom amidst societal constraints.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Life in the groove defeats my revival
